Package: spxlvb
Type: Package
Title: Parameter Exploded Variational Bayes for Linear Regression with
    High-Dimensional Variable Selection and Spike-and-Slab Priors
Version: 0.0.0.9007
Authors@R: c(
    person("Peter", "Olejua", , "polejua@email.sc.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Alexander", "Mclain", , "mclaina@mailbox.sc.edu", role = c("aut")))
Description: Implements parameter exploded variational Bayes (SPXLVB) for
    sparse linear regression with spike-and-slab priors. A coordinate-ascent
    variational inference algorithm with a parameter explosion step that
    rescales variational parameters at each coordinate update, improving
    convergence over standard mean-field updates.
